engineSoundEntity.title: Engine Sound Entity
engineSoundEntity.description: Entity with Sound component (defaults to baseEntity if empty)

description.default: A piece of trash that needs proper disposal.

uiScreenEntity.description: Reference to the global UIScreen entity

imageAsset.description: Texture image to show in UI image element

pickupSoundSource.description: Entity with Sound component and a pre-made pickup slot

pickupSlotName.description: Name of the sound slot to play on pickupSoundSource

cameraOffset.title: Camera Offset
cameraOffset.description: The local space offset with respect to the target entity coordinate system

lerpAmount.title: Lerp Amount
lerpAmount.description: The amount to lerp the camera towards its desired position over time. The closer it is to 1, the faster the camera will move. Lerping is frame rate independent and will be correct for every frame rate.

counterText.description: Text element that shows picked-up trash amount

trashSpawnsParent.description: Parent entity with spawn point children

trashItemsParent.description: Parent entity with trash item prototypes

tutorialScreen.description: Tutorial UI root entity shown when the scene starts

resultText.description: Text element that displays the final result message

resultText2.description: Secondary text element that displays the final result message

panelEntity.description: UI panel that shows the image + buttons

images.description: Textures to show in the carousel

clickSoundSlot.description: Sound slot name to play on click

sceneName.description: Name of the scene to load (as in the editor)

startsNewTrashRound.description: If true, fires "trash:newRound" after loading this scene
